{
  "page": "Feature quote/47",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>“Careful with those, you don’t want to get blood all over those pretty white cloaks.” —<a href=\"/index.php/Bronn\" title=\"Bronn\">Bronn</a> to the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a>, when <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion</a> rescues <a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Baratheon\" title=\"Joffrey Baratheon\">Joffrey</a>’s cruelty<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_32\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 32\">Chapter 32</a>, Sansa III.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404010933\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.007 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.007 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 62/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8414/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 301/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 22/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 525/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    3.894      1 -total\n100.00%    3.894      1 Template:Ref\n 61.97%    2.413      1 Template:Ref/core\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:2500-0!can